
This directory contains scripts for developpers who want to contribute
to this module.


Contributing
============

Please follow the coding style guide:

    PEP 0008 -- Style Guide for Python Code
    https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/


Tests
=====

At the moment, the examples provided in ~BGWpy/Examples
serve as a test suite for this module.
The script run_examples.sh can be executed from the Examples directory.
The script sync_examples_references.sh can be executed from the Examples
directory to update the reference files.

When possible, unit tests should be added so that they can be
executed with nosetests.

